snippet.title: Dino Skeletal Slime Chamber - Search The Slime Build the Dinosaur
snippet.description:
Dino Skeletal Slime Chamber - Search The Slime Build the Dinosaur!  This was fun to learn about and show on video.

Item provided by Uncle Milton for review.



Lucky Penny Thoughts: Some of my favorite things!  Slime and dinosaurs in one toy.  When you get the set, the dinosaur is in pieces in the slime chamber.  Gather your pieces, build the dino and then put him back in the slime.  Thanks 

Later!
LPS-Dave
